---
// about.astro - Aboutページ + 免責事項
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="About Coffee Gear Archive — the definitive database of coffee brewing equipment for home baristas and coffee enthusiasts worldwide."
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1 class="page-header__title">About</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="article-layout">
      <h2>Coffee Gear Archive</h2>
      <p>
        Coffee Gear Archive is the definitive online database for coffee brewing equipment.
        We catalog and review gear from the world's finest coffee equipment makers — from
        Hario's iconic V60 to Fellow's design-forward kettles, Comandante's precision hand
        grinders, and everything in between.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our mission is to help home baristas, coffee enthusiasts, and professionals worldwide
        find the perfect brewing equipment for their needs. We provide detailed specifications,
        brew method comparisons, and honest reviews based on real-world usage.
      </p>

      <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
      <p>
        Unlike generic review sites, we specialize exclusively in coffee brewing equipment. Our
        brew method database with radar charts helps you understand exactly what each method offers.
        Our comparison tool lets you put any two pieces of gear side by side. And our magazine
        articles go deep into the craft, science, and art of brewing better coffee.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        Coffee Gear Archive is a participant in affiliate programs including Amazon Associates.
        This means we may earn a small commission when you purchase through our links, at no
        additional cost to you. This helps us maintain and improve this resource.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our reviews and recommendations are independent. Affiliate relationships never influence
        our ratings or which gear we recommend.
      </p>

      <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        The information provided on Coffee Gear Archive is for general informational purposes
        only. While we strive for accuracy, prices, availability, and specifications may change
        without notice. We are not responsible for any purchasing decisions made based on our content.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Have questions, corrections, or suggestions? We'd love to hear from you.
        <br />Email: info@coffeegeararchive.com
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
